# thoth_browser_provider

Configures browser policy provider integration for a tenant.

## Example Usage

```terraform
resource "thoth_browser_provider" "chrome" {
  provider = "chrome"
  enabled  = true
  config_json = jsonencode({
    tenant = "acme"
  })
}
```
